{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"label 語法","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/orphaned/Web/JavaScript/Obsolete_Pages/Obsolete_Pages/Obsolete_Pages/循環語法/label_語法","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"label_語法","title":"label 語法","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>label</code> 提供識別子作為語法，可讓你的程式的任何一處都能參考得到。舉例來說，你可以使用標籤來標識循環，然後使用 <code>break</code> 或 <code>continue</code> 語法來指示程式是否要中斷循環或繼續執行。</p>\n<p><code>label</code> 語法如下︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">label&nbsp;:\n   statement\n</pre>\n<p><code>label</code> 的值可以是任意的 JavaScript 識別子，只要不是保留字的話都可以使用。使用標籤來標識的 <code>statement</code> 可以是任意的語句。</p>\n<p><strong>範例</strong><br>\n 在以下範例中，標籤 <code>markLoop</code> 標識了 while 循環。</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">markLoop:\nwhile (theMark == true)\n   doSomething();\n}\n</pre>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n <p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/循環語法/while_語法\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/循環語法/break_語法\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"label 提供識別子作為語法，可讓你的程式的任何一處都能參考得到。舉例來說，你可以使用標籤來標識循環，然後使用 break 或 continue 語法來指示程式是否要中斷循環或繼續執行。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","source":{"folder":"zh-tw/orphaned/web/javascript/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/循環語法/label_語法","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/orphaned/web/javascript/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/循環語法/label_語法/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"label 語法 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}